basic.Peptide Name: So-pis (S. ocellatus piscidin, natural AMPs; fish, animals, UCLL1)
basic.Source: Red drum, redfish, channel bass, puppy drum, spottail bass,Sciaenops ocellatus
basic.Target Organism: All tested bacteria and yeast were resistant to synthetic So-pis at the tested concentrations. However, it showed activity against  C. irritans trophonts and theronts (killed 20% at 12 uM in 60 min, 83% at 24 uM in 30 min, and 100% at 48 uM or 96 uM in 15 min).
